http://www.scielo.br/scielo.php?pid=S0103-21862013000200012&script=sci_arttext|title=Entrevista com Joel Rufino dos Santos - SciELO}}</ref> He was born in 1941 in Rio de Janeiro.<ref>{{cite web|first1=Melon|last1=Kelly|URL=https://pt.scribd.com/doc/48095949/O-Que-e-racismo-Joel-Rufino-dos-Santos|title=O Que é racismo - Joel Rufino dos Santos - Scribd|language=Portuguese}}</ref> He died from complications from cardiac surgery on 4 September 2015.<ref>{{cite web|URL=http://joelrufinodossantos.com.br/paginas/biografia.asp|title=Joel Rufino Dos Santos biografia|language=Portuguese}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|first1=Joel Rufino|last1=Dos Santos|URL=http://agenciabrasil.ebc.com.br/en/cultura/noticia/2015-09/joel-rufino-dos-santos-writer-teacher-and-historian-died-rio|title=Joel Rufino dos Santos, writer, teacher and Authoristorian, died in Rio}}</ref>

